{
  "name": "SparklineGroup",
  "summary": "<p><strong>SparklineGroup</strong> 对象可包含多个迷你图以及该迷你图组的属性设置，例如颜色和轴设置。每个迷你图都由一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Sparkline/Sparkline .htm#Sparkline.Sparkline\">Sparkline</a></strong> 对象表示。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.Modify\">Modify</a></strong> 方法可在迷你图组中添加或删除迷你图。使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.ModifyLocation\">ModifyLocation</a></strong> 方法可更改迷你图的位置，使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.ModifySourceData\">ModifySourceData</a></strong> 方法则可以更改源数据所在的区域。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例会在 A1:A4 处创建一组绑定到 Sheet1!B1:E4 区域中的源数据的列迷你图，并更改系列颜色以便用红色显示各个列。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlSparkColumn, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1!B1:E4&quot;</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SeriesColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组中迷你图的高点是否可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Points</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Highpoint</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表一组迷你图。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Axes",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回关联的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkAxes/SparkAxes .htm#SparkAxes.SparkAxes\">SparkAxes</a></strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组垂直轴的MinScaleType属性是否为xlSparkScaleGroup。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Vertical</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MinScaleType</span> == xlSparkScaleGroup)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组设置为按右至左顺序在水平轴上绘制点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightToLeftPlotOrder</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "SparkAxes",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回迷你图组中的迷你图数。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 I1 上第一个迷你图组中迷你图的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "DateRange",
      "summary": "<p>若要清除日期范围，请将此属性设置为空字符串。</p>\n<p>日期范围必须是连续的一维范围。</p>\n<p>日期范围可以在不同于 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.Location\">Location</a></strong> 和 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.SourceData\">SourceData</a></strong> 属性的工作表上。</p>\n<p>日期范围中的空单元格和非日期值不显示。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>获取或设置迷你图组的日期范围。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的日期范围。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DateRange</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的日期范围。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DateRange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:F1&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayBlanksAs",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>获取或设置空白单元格在迷你图组中的绘制方式。可以是 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlDisplayBlanksAs 枚举.html\">XlDisplayBlanksAs</a></strong> 常量之一。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的DisplayBlanksAs属性是否为xlNotPlotted。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayBlanksAs</span> == xlNotPlotted)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的DisplayBlanksAs属性。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayBlanksAs</span> = xlInterpolated\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlDisplayBlanksAs",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayHidden",
      "summary": "<p>如果隐藏单元格在迷你图组中显示，则为 <strong>True</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>指定是否在迷你图组中绘制隐藏单元格。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组设置为绘制隐藏单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayHidden</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组是否绘制隐藏单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayHidden</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "LineWeight",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>获取或设置迷你图组中迷你图的粗细。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的迷你图的粗细。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineWeight</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的迷你图的粗细。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineWeight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Location",
      "summary": "<p>迷你图组中所有迷你图的位置必须在同一个工作表上，但迷你图组的源数据可以在不同的工作表或工作簿上。</p>\n<p>代表 <strong>Location</strong> 属性的区域大小必须等于 <strong>SparklineGroup</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.SourceData\">SourceData</a></strong> 属性中的行数或列数。</p>\n<p>与迷你图组关联的连续区域只能是一维的。如果区域是不连续的，则必须分别指定每个单元格。</p>\n<p>不要使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Union\">Union</a></strong> 方法创建非连续区域，因为 <strong>Union</strong> 方法返回单个区域引用。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>获取或设置代表迷你图组的位置的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的位置的地址。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Location</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的位置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Location</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PlotBy",
      "summary": "<p>只有在迷你图所基于的数据处于方形区域中时，才可以设置此属性，例如，数据位于区域 A1:B2。</p>\n<p>方形区域中数据的默认值为按行绘制数据 (<strong>xlSparklineRowsSquare</strong>)。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置当迷你图所基于的数据处于方形区域中时，如何绘制迷你图。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 I1 中第一个迷你图组的PlotBy属性是否为xlSparklineNonSquare。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PlotBy</span> == xlSparklineNonSquare)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格区域 I1:J1 中第一个迷你图组的PlotBy属性。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1:J1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SparklineGroups</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PlotBy</span> = xlSparklineRowsSquare\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSparklineRowCol 枚举.html\">XlSparklineRowCol</a></strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Points",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回迷你图组的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkPoints/SparkPoints .htm#SparkPoints.SparkPoints\">SparkPoints</a></strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
